g":"有咁多時間長篇大論放灰，就唔該抽少少出黎打幾隻字<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>提提啲人而家未撤，隨時攞得返出黎</strong></span><br />\n個個都肯提下啲人咪知囉？二百萬人入面有好多係關心時事既新手<br />\n啱啱先訓醒既人中晒文字遊戲既伏有幾出奇？"},{"pid":"b58db4f6f8649f43569ed93f5130596523089ccd","tid":1241953,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b52d3eb60e79b277822f901a8cf256c71e528db","tid":1241953,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"成日都睇到叫人唔好灰既post<br />\n但根本見唔到幾個篤灰post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五毛新策略?係咁叫人唔好放棄令人以為真係已經失敗左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"好撚多放灰post喎"},{"pid":"eaf66a4ffd7bf5c9b75d4601b2470a8da5de29f8","tid":1241953,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"[/quote]係咩？想知有咩例子[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3OVSVV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3OVSVV.jpg&h=df588540&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3s2jz9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3s2jz9f.jpg&h=ba23693e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCnvGPg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCnvGPg.jpg&h=a5d4a648&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vb9eo2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVb9eo2B.png&h=7ad5172e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79afd3a86906fb30b56fe31bd44b33fcc4fcda6d","tid":1241953,"uid":147047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"身邊個個都話佢等於無講過野"},{"pid":"e2089b80be9b28999d51b77f5302c22967fa37dc","tid":1241953,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:41:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1a29aadfd0a3375b4ca7c3ae7a0374b9757d9887","tid":1241953,"uid":21